Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:17.40,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.49,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:38.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:51.59,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:54.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.38,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:05.29,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:11.26,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:17.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.50,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.65,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:25.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:31.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:36.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:36.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:43.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:50.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:56.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.57,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:08.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:25.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼 趁早别当什么骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早真够刻苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑术要靠日积月累
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候起一天都没荒废过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨子里的死用功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在夸人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 但是刚才的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用卢克打造的刀时需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀的使用方法别具一格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想熟练使用 必须先从掌握这个动作开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择这把剑的目的正在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要得到卢克打造的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 正所谓爱的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 看来需要和你认真谈一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.10,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur3}誓约 -Promise-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又钻进我被窝里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉抱起来舒适到家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快被融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是软软的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想收做我的专用枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它当作武器使用多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他看看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要卢克的一两把刀算得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别总是纠结人家的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚的不也很大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 我说那把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的使用者手中 我可能会成为残忍的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 塞西莉不会那么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会为保护别人使用我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果主人是塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的风一定也会更美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有那一天的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 尽在自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天生胆小 是个剑术不精的蹩脚骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也有资格成为你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做我的朋友好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 选我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士绝不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是爱的告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也希望塞西莉做我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说 非你莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗 我这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑绝不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是爱的告白吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知危险却无可奈何吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑备受瞩目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时撤架会影响客源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过确实 一想到会有恶魔闹事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难免心中不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望尽量避免出现死者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话已出口很难收回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么至少由我承担责任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样 骑士也必须全力以赴保护市民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们背负着的「永恒的矛盾」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着眼现实 但时刻高举理想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果想必会造成众多部下的伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不得不做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以魔剑为饵 诱出黑衣男子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断绝一切祸根
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有特别任务给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的拍卖会上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你现场演示魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 你面对相悖的命题…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说吧 好比你有一位发誓要保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但情况迫使你让她冒险 你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会提些为难人的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的话 不会让他冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果无法避免的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭上性命也要保护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了 突然问些莫名其妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能会让你冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 刚成为朋友就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们不让我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算拿你当诱饵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我相信塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我一定会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你的未来在于魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要…魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才对 去得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑只属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑…魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑…想要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是最强的魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪婪的Basilard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:19.78,test,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs28}Basilard：瑞士起源的短剑，刀刃薄而锋利， 除战场突刺外常被用于切割食物和砍伐的万能武器。名称来源于瑞士西北部省会Basel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要专门去竞拍 先来先得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 买吧买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的 应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊卢克 有火喷出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也没件像样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的凑齐一百把 也许能有所作为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打败那家伙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张啊 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 表现抢眼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时求婚的人怕是会踏破门槛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我自我介绍的环节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有这么大的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和胸部无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞什么 卢克肯定也在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示自己的风采吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳房也好 胸部也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专指那些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 那种性格扭曲的守财奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当不留情面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想来关心一下就是这种回报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太傻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉小姐 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太上心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人出现 让市民避难 我们打倒敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已 简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是今天的主角 魔剑登场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「解开沉眠 寻求真实 风凝吾手」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以弑神」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人变成剑的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑不仅仅局限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑平地生风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑 魔剑 魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 我就能得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑 我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妇女孩子优先 快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市外来的客人去二号街
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「光明啊 赐君以死」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以精灵契约之名 毁灭不净之物」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵祈祷班 吐血也得给我吟唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有不通人情到忘记招待客人的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 汉尼拔这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为战争的幸存者 好好叙叙旧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死老头 有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也是我选中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把魔剑给我带来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上骑士团的志气 绝不放你离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃吧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 阿丽亚她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去救阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃你也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发过誓要保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在的我没那个能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给我力量吧 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要对你的能力不足负责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都…没有做成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要一无所成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 借给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想要 我愿献上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要钱的话 为你干活到死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要身体的话 任你摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也替她求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能对阿丽亚见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该明白的 因为阿丽亚和我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮她不就是了吗 帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夺回阿丽亚 只有打败它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的火焰连铁都能溶化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的刀至多能剥下它的火皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最后一击 要由你来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔 你能下得了手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原本也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锻造开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水挫 小割 选别 积重 锻造
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折返 折返 折返 折返
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用剑夺人性命 就无法保护他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是骑士的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收柄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的对手 最多只能砍三刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这把刀的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切开它火焰的瞬间 你去扎下致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会仅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的话 你必死无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样也要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士绝不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“信者得救赎”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在过去战争中受过怎样的苦难 我无从得知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 快宰了它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么拯救 无疑是自不量力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我也要发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要救助这双眼中看到的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这世上有光与影的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要始终站到光明的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀揣梦想 战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 刚才确实看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男子 又给他逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}斯特拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他借风声这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}斯特拉达 我是塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杀你的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不要忘记我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也永远不会忘记你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风告诉了我 他的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不会忘记”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对逝去的39位宝贵的生命 从心底献上哀悼与致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有责任在我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为不让这样的悲剧重演 铭刻在心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造和平的城镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑招来死亡 唤来灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而人们又不愿放弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站会是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿也有塞西莉这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有下一站
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后继续由我来护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 你决不是专门伤人的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是守护之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我 成为一把和我共同守护这座城市的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做我的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做我的战友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听候吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以剑芒为誓 与您约定
